comments:
Renamed 1.5.1968 to become the parish of Newton Poppleford & Harpford. 
    See also Table 2, notes (b) and (c).

Abolished 1.4.1974 and added to the East Devon unparished 
    area. See also Table 2, notes (c) and (i).

Created 1.5.1968 by renaming the parish of Harpford. See also 
    Table 2, note (j).

Abolished 1.4.1966 and divided between the parishes of Exeter and 
    Broad Clyst. See also Table 2, notes (c), (e), (f) and (g).

Abolished 1.4.1966 and divided between the parishes of Exeter, 
    Clyst St. George and Woodbury. See also Table 2, notes (c), (e) and (g).

Abolished 1.4.1974 and added to the East Devon unparished 
    area. See also Table 2, notes (c) and (i).
